Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi...\N- Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari kita mulakan!\NJangan biarkan dia terlepas, Komuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.\N- Tak nak! Ia menyakitkanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tak nak!
